title: Money Bank 3D

creator: tastypill
descriptionHtml:
What if you had decided to become a bank teller? Find out if you’d be good at it by slipping into the simulation role of a banker.

A fun way to cure your boredom and keep your brain entertained by taking care of customers, validating checks, depositing money, sorting coins, keeping your coworkers and customers safe during bank heists and much more!

Are you ready to prove that you have what it takes to run a bank?

Features:
- Over 1000 levels of fun and entertaining bank teller tasks
- Improve and boost your mathematical and cognitive skill
- Rewards for completing tasks
- Variety of fun mini-games to challenge your brain
- Game autosaves, so you can pick up where you left off
- Get awesome upgrades and prices for your bank
- Build your own office with fun 3D furniture and accessories

Fun for all ages! Money Bank 3D is an entertaining game for everyone. Improve your mathematical and cognitive skills while fulfilling the tasks of a bank teller.

How To Play:
- Swipe right/left to approve checks and emails
- Tap on bills to withdraw the correct amount
- Tap and hold to count money
- Tap to insert credit card
- Tap to type in pins and amounts
- Sign checks and documents by following the line with your finger
- Swipe to insert checks
- Tap and drag money to sort it
- Tap and drag numbers to copy passcodes for locks
- Tap to unlock doors
- Tap the SOS button that lights up when the robber isn’t looking
- Tap on money to throw into the crowd


Fulfill the typical tasks of a bank teller in this fun and entertaining bank simulator mobile game.

It’s a great way to pass the time and improve your math skills. Check back frequently for exciting new updates and features!
descriptionShort: The banking game where you run your own bank!
